            5.9.5 (RT#86989)

0.002     2013-07-16 22:31:11 PDT-0700 (Karen Etheridge)
          - name, description, and always_recommend options are now prefaced
            with dashes, just like -phase and -relationship (to avoid naming
            conflicts)

